title: #92:  Robots, Reptilians and Grizzles Oh My with Steebee Weebee
description:
Welcome to another episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli. This episode Sam and Ryan welcome from the Steebee Weebee show, Steve Lee. This episode we discuss...
1) Mangchi at the Grizzly Festival
2) The Steebee Weebee Show
3) DAARP
4) Artificial Intelligence
5) Ghost
6) Simulation Theory
7) Jesus Vs Ghosts
Thank you for listening
